      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "お、おはようございます、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "G-good morning‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "天動さん？　あぁ、おはよう\nどうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ good morning‚ Tendo.\nWhat’s the matter?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　な、何がですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?! Wh-what do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.9841724872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "打ち合わせは午後からだぞ？\n時間まで、まだ三時間もあるんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your briefing session is in the afternoon‚ isn’t it?\nBut you’re here three hours early.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "え、えぇ、まぁ……\nその……時間まですることがないので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Er‚ well…\nI… didn’t have anything to do before that‚ so…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "めずらしいな、天動さんは少しでも時間があれば\nレッスンスタジオに行ってるのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What a rare sight. You usually spend\nwhat free time you have at the studio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9425623418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "うっ。そ、そうですね\nレッスンも大切なんですが、今は――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-you’re right.\nLessons are important‚ but right now—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、ですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "天動さん、立ってないで座ったら？\nそれか向こうの橋本さんと話でもしてくれば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about taking a seat?\nOr if you’re looking for Satomi…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.5671655497,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、は、はい。ですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ eh‚ well…. I mean…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……もしかして、何かあったのか？\nここでは話せないようなこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is something wrong?\nSomething you’re not comfortable talking about here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.7548756441,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "いっ……いえ、そんなことは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… not exactly… but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}